headline: NYSE Content Advisory:  Celebrating Singapore's 60th Anniversary - A Milestone of Progress
summary: The New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) today extends its heartfelt congratulations to the Republic of Singapore on the occasion of its 60th National Day, celebrated annually on August 9th.
